Question 1.Question: A world Title Boxing contest took place in New York [750W time zone] on a Tuesday between 21:30 and 22:30 hours and was televised live. When did viewers in Lagos [150E time zone] watch the contest live on television?
Question 1.Explanation:
Longitudinal difference between New York 75oW and Lagos 15oE is 90o convert 90o to time = 90/15 = 6 hours.

Since we are moving west we subtract 21.30 hours – 6 hours = 15.30, 22.30 – 6 hours = 16.30

Viewers in Lagos will watch the contest on Tuesday between 15:30 and 16:30 hours.
